---
title: Nan's Chicken & Creamy Apple Slaw with Crushed Lemon & Parmesan Potatoes
description: Nan's special seasoning has done it again! We've teamed tonight's flavour-packed chicken breast strips with all the essentials:
lemony crushed potatoes, super crunchy slaw and of course, a creamy mayo.
